  <h2>Common PDF Problems &amp; Solutions</h2>

  <h3>Problem: PDF won't open</h3>
  <p><strong>Possible causes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>File is corrupted</li>
    <li>PDF is password-protected</li>
    <li>Incompatible PDF version</li>
