  <p><strong>Solutions:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Try opening in a different PDF viewer (Adobe Reader, Chrome, Firefox)</li>
    <li>Ask the sender for the password</li>
    <li>Re-download the file (may have been corrupted during download)</li>
  </ul>

